title: [Vornavis, Outlands Road]
description: Twisted laurel trees and scrub dot the plains here, becoming more numerous to the northeast where the grassland gives way to hills.  Beyond the unevenness of foothills to the north snow-capped mountain peaks stand pale beneath the stars.

Twisted laurel trees and scrub dot the plains here, becoming more numerous to the northeast where the grassland gives way to hills.  Beyond the unevenness of foothills to the north white-topped mountain peaks seem almost to hang in the sky.
